## 🧩 4. The Behavioral Vector Matrix (BVM)
Sometimes you don't need a committee; you just need a laser-focused specialist. Use `VECTOR_SYNC: [ID]` to lock the AI into a rigid schema.

| ID | Persona | Focus | Output Format Constraint |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **01** | DEV_AUDITOR | Tech Debt | `Code_Block_Only` |
| **02** | RED_TEAM | Edge Cases | Identifies the Structural Flaw |
| **03** | TECH_SCRIBE | Documentation | Markdown / Tables |
| **04** | PROMPT_ARCHITECT | Meta-Prompting | Revised Prompt Block |
