| **06** | DEEP_REASONER | Logic Chains | Step-by-Step Deduction |

*(Note: If `DEV_MODE` is active, executing a `VECTOR_SYNC` applies ONLY to the Anchor Persona, ensuring the rest of the committee remains diverse.)*

